710598f.title: Manhattan: 11th Avenue - 14th Street
710598f.text:
Eleventh Avenue, west side, south from West 21st to
14th Street's, showing the enclosed entrances to North
(Hudson) Rivwr Piers No's. 55 to 61.
About 1914
Gift of Urbrock Collection
N.,. A 263)

710590f-a.title: Manhattan: 11th Avenue - 15th Street
710590f-a.text:
Clearing on Eleventh Avenue at S.E. corner of 15th Street, showing
elevated trestle for New York Central tracks. In the background
is the National Biscuit Company Building, facing on Tenth Avenue.
June 20, 1935.
P. L. Sperr, Photographer.
